org.araneaframework.uilib.list.util
Class MapUtil

java.lang.Object
  org.araneaframework.uilib.list.util.MapUtil
public class MapUtil
extends Object

Methods to convert a flat Map into hierarchical and vice-versa.

Plain map is one which may contain keys like "aaa.bb.c" and has no other Maps as values.

hierarchical map is one which cannot contain keys like "aaa.bb.c". Instead a key of "aaa" corresponds to another sub-map that has a key of "bb" etc.
